ed="T" n="0774c28"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0774c28"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000016619"><placeName>池州</placeName><placeName>南泉院</placeName></placeName><persName key="A003889">普願</persName><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n2650"/>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0774c29"/><persName key="A003889">釋普願</persName>，俗姓<name>王</name>，<placeName key="PL000000023249"><placeName>鄭州</placeName><placeName>新鄭</placeName></placeName>人也。其宗嗣於<placeName key="PL000000018627">江<pb ed="T" n="0775a" xml:id="T50.2061.0775a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0775a01"/>西</placeName><persName key="A003623">大寂</persName>，<persName key="A003623">大寂</persName>師<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName><persName key="A004015">觀音讓</persName>，<persName key="A004015">讓</persName>則<persName key="A001719">曹溪</persName>之<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz1"/>冡<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz1"/><lb
ed="T" n="0775a02"/>子<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1129"/>也，於<persName key="A003889">願</persName>為<anchor xml:id="beg0775001"/>大<anchor xml:id="end0775001"/>父<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1306"/>，其高、曾可知也，則<persName key="A003889">南泉</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0775a03"/>之禪有自來矣。<persName key="A003889">願</persName>在孕，母不喜葷血。<date from-iso="+0757-01-29" key="j19975771997960" to-iso="+0758-02-16"><name>至德</name><lb
ed="T" n="0775a04"/>二年</date>，跪請於父母乞出家，脫然有去覊鞅<lb
ed="T" n="0775a05"/>之色。乃投<placeName key="PL000000023209"><placeName>密縣</placeName><placeName>大隈山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A018083">大慧<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n1481"/>受業。苦<lb
ed="T" n="0775a06"/>節篤勵，胼胝皸瘃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1561"/>，不敢為身主，其<ref type="person" target="#A018083">師</ref>異<ref type="person" target="#A003889">之</ref>。<lb
ed="T" n="0775a07"/><date from-iso="+0777-02-17" key="j20049012005254" to-iso="+0778-02-05"><name>大曆</name>十二年</date>，<persName key="A003889">願</persName>春秋三十矣，詣<placeName key="PL000000023256"><placeName>嵩山</placeName><placeName>會善寺</placeName></placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0775a08"/><persName key="A010498">暠<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>受具，習<placeName key="PL000000024082">相部</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2176"/>舊章<ptr target="#n903"/>，究毘尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>篇聚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g582"/>之<lb
ed="T" n="0775a09"/>學。後遊講肆，上《楞伽》<ptr target="#n94"/>頂，入《華嚴》海會，抉《中》<ptr target="#n1551"/>、<lb
ed="T" n="0775a10"/>《百》<ptr target="#n1552"/>、《門》<ptr target="#n1553"/>觀之關鑰，領玄機於疏、論之外。當其<lb
ed="T" n="0775a11"/>鋒者，皆旗靡轍亂<ptr target="#n1554"/>。<persName key="A003623">大寂</persName>門下八百餘人，每參<lb
ed="T" n="0775a12"/>聽之後，尋繹<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1818"/>師說，是非紛錯。<persName key="A003889">願</persName>或自默而<lb
ed="T" n="0775a13"/>語，群論皆弭曰：「夫人不言乃言爾耳。」自後<lb
ed="T" n="0775a14"/><anchor xml:id="beg0775002"/>含<anchor xml:id="end0775002"/>景<ptr type="glossary" target="#g41"/>匿耀，似不能言者，人以其無法說，<lb
ed="T" n="0775a15"/>或扣其關，亦堅拒不洩。時有密賾<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g331"/>其機者，<lb
ed="T" n="0775a16"/>微露頭角，乃知其非無法說，時未至矣。<date from-iso="+0795-01-30" key="j20114572011840" to-iso="+0796-02-17"><name>貞<lb
ed="T" n="0775a17"/>元</name>十一年</date>，<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>拄</sic><corr>挂</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz2"/>錫<placeName key="PL000000016614"><placeName>池陽</placeName><placeName>南泉山</placeName></placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0775003"/>堙<anchor xml:id="end0775003"/>谷刊木，以<lb
ed="T" n="0775a18"/>構禪宇，簑笠飯牛，溷<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1562"/>于牧童。斫山畬田，種<lb
ed="T" n="0775a19"/>食以饒。足不下<placeName key="PL000000016614">南泉</placeName>三十年矣。夫洪鐘不<lb
ed="T" n="0775a20"/>為<anchor xml:id="beg0775004"/>莛<anchor xml:id="end0775004"/>撞發聲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1563"/>，聲之者，故有待矣<ptr target="#n1557"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0827-03-18" key="j20231922024000" notAfter-iso="+0829-06-03"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz3"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz3"/>和</name>年<lb
ed="T" n="0775a21"/>初</date>，<placeName key="PL000000016955">宣</placeName>使<persName key="A010473">陸<roleName>公</roleName>亘</persName><ptr target="#n1555"/>、前<placeName key="PL000000016923">池陽</placeName>太守皆知其抗迹塵<lb
ed="T" n="0775a22"/>外，為四方法眼，與護軍<placeName key="PL000000009523">彭城</placeName><persName key="A010499">劉<roleName>公</roleName></persName>同迎請<lb
ed="T" n="0775a23"/>下<ref type="place" target="#PL000000016614">山</ref>，北面申<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz4"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz4"/>。不經再歲，毳衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1417"/>之子奔走<lb
ed="T" n="0775a24"/>道途，不下數百人。<date key="j20260052026005" when-iso="+0834-11-29"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz5"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz5"/>和</name>甲寅歲十月二十一<lb
ed="T" n="0775a25"/>日</date>示疾。<date key="j20260662026066" when-iso="+0835-01-29">十二月二十三日</date>，有白虹貫於禪<lb
ed="T" n="0775a26"/>室後峯，占之者：得非<ref type="person" target="#A003889">南泉</ref>謝世乎？是日西<lb
ed="T" n="0775a27"/>峯，巨石崩，聲數十里。當晝，有乳虎遶禪林<lb
ed="T" n="0775a28"/>而號，眾咸異之。<date key="j20260682026068" when-iso="+0835-01-31">二十五日</date>東方明，告門人<lb
ed="T" n="0775a29"/>曰：「星翳燈幻亦久矣，勿謂<ref type="person" target="#A003889">吾</ref>有去來也。」言<pb ed="T" n="0775b" xml:id="T50.2061.0775b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0775b01"/>訖而謝，春秋八十七，僧臘五十八<ptr target="#n1556"/>。<persName key="A010500">契元</persName>、<persName key="A009804">文暢</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0775b02"/>等凡九百人，皆布衣墨巾，泣血于山門。赴喪<lb
ed="T" n="0775b03"/>會葬者相繼<anchor xml:id="beg0775005"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0775005"/>路，哀號之聲震于崖谷。<date from-iso="+0835-02-06" key="j20260742026427" to-iso="+0836-01-25">乙<lb
ed="T" n="0775b04"/>卯歲</date>，門人奉全身於靈塔，從其教也。膳部<lb
ed="T" n="0775b05"/>員外郎史館修撰<persName key="A010303">劉軻</persName>欽若前烈，追德頌美<lb
ed="T" n="0775b06"/>焉。</p>
